title: Miss Sophie Lee & New Orleans Jazz Vipers - 2006 - Self-Titl
description:
Miss Sophie Lee & New Orleans Jazz Vipers - 2006 - Self-Titled

Born and raised in the Chicago area, Miss Sophie Lee moved to New Orleans in 2001 in search of its rich musical and culinary culture. She quickly found Frenchmen Street and the New Orleans Jazz Vipers who along with Bart Ramsey, collaborated with her on her first New Orleans self-titled CD in 2006.

Track list:
01 Stairway To The Stars
02 Am I Blue
03 I Want To Be Happy
04 Blue Skies
05 Me Myself And I
06 Bread And Gravy
07 Sugar Pie
08 I Must Have That Man
09 Goodnight My Love

Enjoy and share!
